PAI Partners completed the sale of
its 69.3 percent stake in Gruppo Coin SpA to  BC Partners  Ltd.
for 644.6 million euros, at 6.50 euros per share, PAI Partnersâ€™
advisers Latham & Watkins said in an e-mailed statement today.
In addition, BC Partners bought a further 9.4 percent stake in
Gruppo Coin in shares held by management and the company, for
87.8 million euros, the statement said. The sale values the
Italian fashion chain at 1.4 billion euros, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
